<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248161>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Desmapsamma vervoorti van Soest, 1998. A, Sponge growing on Carijoa riisei in situ; B, Reticulated surface of the sponge with large amount of sediment; C, Regular ectosomal skeleton of tracts of oxeas and sand grains; D, Choanosomal skeleton of tracts of oxeas organised in a rather irregular reticulum; E, Oxea and close up of the extremities; F, Isochela I; G, Isochela II; H, Sigma I; I, Sigma II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248161/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

